":"2017-06-24T15:14:37.000Z","msg":"好靚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都好想練靚手字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經成日寫notes 但都做唔到隻隻字筆風一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1651f1af41a03ef1731878d6296cd735d01383b","tid":294251,"uid":87910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:16:50.000Z","msg":"我愛你愛到肚子痛。<br />\n我是如此愛你，愛到水龍頭流出海水。<br />\n我愛你愛到肚子裡有三顆樹，連鞋子也會自己走路。<br />\n我愛你愛到脖子落枕扭成今日焗烤。<br />\n我愛你。<br />\n可唔可以寫比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df28205f532a60a55cf5458896ca99e6332062c","tid":294251,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:17:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>潘柏霖<br />\n 無抄足全首 節錄<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/24/225331_2a63e0a7d4b928887a4abb575b5222a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F24%2F225331_2a63e0a7d4b928887a4abb575b5222a6.jpg&h=d4e97b5c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/24/225337_25606511a5ed2c1ab22f073d7b972b28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F24%2F225337_25606511a5ed2c1ab22f073d7b972b28.jpg&h=61c549af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我想要好好<br />\n再去愛一個人<br />\n替他織一條圍巾<br />\n想和他好好度過一個冬天<br />\n我想要勇敢<br />\n<br />\n我想和自己好好道歉<br />\n好好再過活幾年<br />\n好好再睡一覺<br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n記得好好愛自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲數我夜啲找<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n情傷"},{"pid":"2bba1eb72d241be754e355163eb2fc0341e63f14","tid":294251,"uid":87910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:38:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我愛你愛到肚子痛。<br />\n我是如此愛你，愛到水龍頭流出海水。<br />\n我愛你愛到肚子裡有三顆樹，連鞋子也會自己走路。<br />\n我愛你愛到脖子落枕扭成今日焗烤。<br />\n我愛你。<br />\n可唔可以寫比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我愛你，愛到肚子裡有三棵樹，鞋子會自己走路，月亮打電話來探問我的消息，脖子落枕扭成今日焗烤。<br />\n我愛你愛到髮絲蕩漾如陽光之下一幅風景，愛到永遠不再有意義。<br />\n抄錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該可唔可以抄比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1024ef50d095a588f061cdc4ce86dffc66476c2a","tid":294251,"uid":81751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T20:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n顧城　避免<br />\n你不願意種花<br />\n你說：<br />\n「我不願看見它<br />\n一點點凋落」<br />\n是的<br />\n為了避免結束<br />\n你避免了一切開始<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28437a3dd9b61bcec86ea1b424cdbd4f415940c","tid":294251,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T21:15:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2bdecb393dcbf58a82ef4f1a5b4a3954b7c092f","tid":294251,"uid":114997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:35:14.000Z","msg":"樓主，手痕想一齊寫，交流下，得嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d43483b789e83e88ebadcfd58b4b532c61d40959","tid":294251,"uid":114997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/234110_3f5664eccd46dbf5645699540ec35a40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F234110_3f5664eccd46dbf5645699540ec35a40.jpg&h=d558d6b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e714b6f6d6424f40878293b79cb616ff9704e1fc","tid":294251,"uid":44065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T18:21:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得罪幫我寫多個「Weak」<br />\n用黑白果枝筆係格仔紙寫<br />\n好似呢個咁<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/24/144633_dc75c7b0f8518ab31e3ad74bb862d05b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2